title: Pretty Hate Machine: 2016 (Tritnew's PHM Remaster)
description:
Pretty Hate Machine: 2016 Is a project I was working with on one stormy windy night, when I was bored and decided "Maybe I'll clean up and remaster PHM", and I did so! I used Audacity with It, I first used a compressor, abjusted It a little, then the equalizer where I cleaned It up and made It sound crystal clear. It's very simple, but I plan on doing a 5.1 Surround Sound version of It sometime, whenever I learn how to do so.

So, here It Is:

Pretty Hate Machine: 2016!

Next release: TBA (Possible It'll be a remastered Broken)
